title: Looking for apartment with League players!
body:
I'm looking for anyone who lives in Sydney, Australia (preferably near the Inner West) that needs a new household member!
I'm only looking for people who play League or other games because I need a place that has decent internet and won't lag if more than 1 person is on the net.

If anyone is interested please contact me.

replies.body: Why would anyone down vote this?
